706900f-a.title: Brooklyn: Stillwell Avenue - Neptune Avenue
706900f-a.text:
Stillwell Ave., east side, north from Neptune Ave., showing the Coney
Island Times building (No. 2753) and before it C. Kelly's auto olacksmith
shop (No. 2761).
November 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
